{"id": "pos057", "name": "Multi_File_P057", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_???_697_12_25]</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "Just one person?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Yes. I'm the only one!\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "... The heck? Isn't this just a brat? Don't call me to the storage room for a brat like this.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member D"], "content": "Director! Even though it's just thugs stealing some unimportant cargo, this has been happening every month. They've been taking our cargo one bit at a time. It must be the Hou Sang Tang people who are doing all this!\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "And why does that matter? I always knew that they've been doing shady tricks like this. Even if they get their dirty paws on our parts, they don't have the technology to present any threat to us.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member D"], "content": "... Then... what should we do with this guy?\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "What do you mean \"what should we do\"? You guys can do whatever you want with him, be it let him go or \"deal\" with him. Hey, what's your name?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "H-Hayato... Hayato Kusu.\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "......\nI think I've seen this name somewhere... Brat, come with me for a bit.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "As I expected. Your guardian, her name is Feng Huang, right?\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "......! Yes... Umm, how did you...\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "Here, she's on the candidate list for our latest medical project.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Medical project...? I thought you guys are part of the underground society. Kyuu Hou Kai and the eight Ravens... I've heard some things about them.\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "We are indeed part of the underground society. However, Node 03 as a whole is part of the underground society. Who do you think provides the admins with the technology you people use every day? Managing the city is a part of our job as well.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "Your grandma, she suffered a brain stroke, correct? She is in a coma right now. Her situation just so happens to match the conditions of a test subject for our latest technology. Perhaps, there's a way to wake her up.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "... Seriously!?\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "But, this is an unstable project that is still in its experimental phase. Both the price and risks are way too high. No one is willing to try, so there's no way for us to continue.\n... What do you think? If you're willing to sign an affidavit that allows her to be our test subject, I will overlook the theft you committed against us.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "......!\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_???_698_03_18]</i>\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Medical Staff"], "content": "I'm sorry. Your grandma's brain nerves were too badly damaged. The experiment has failed. However, it's not a complete failure either. We've successfully restored all her senses except vision. You can interact with her through this interface. Her thoughts will be presented to you through words and synthetic voices.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "......!? Please activate it right away!\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Medical Staff"], "content": "I must remind you... the experiment failed. If you activate it now, she will only live for another two minutes... However, even if you just leave her like this, you don't know when she'll pass away too. The decision is yours to make.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "......!\n... <i>*Sobs*</i>...\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward 30 minutes»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "I... I've made my decision...\nPlease activate it. However... before that, I would like the nurse to help me with something...\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Feng]"], "content": "This is...? Where am I? It's so dark...\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Grandma! It's me, Hayato! Can you feel it? My hand.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Feng]"], "content": "<i>Hayato...</i>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Bottle_Open", "Opens bottle"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Feng]"], "content": "This... scent... Kaori?... Is it Kaori!? Where are you!?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Kaori]"], "content": "<i>Grandma!</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nurse"], "content": "...... (Holds hand)\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Feng]"], "content": "<i>Kaori! Hayato has found you? You're back? I... I can feel it... your hand...</i>\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nurse"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "... Grandma, Kaori has come back.\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Feng]"], "content": "<i>I knew it... You're a brave girl. You're still alive... I knew Hayato would definitely find you... Ah... thank you... thank the lord...</i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Yes. You don't need to worry anymore. You no longer have to cry yourself to sleep every night...\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Feng]"], "content": "<i>Good... Thank... goodness...</i>\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Medical Staff"], "content": "The time... is up.\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">You can... finally, sleep with a smile. You can sleep with a smile, forever... <i>*Sobs*...</i></font> <font size=\"3.6\">WAAAHHHHHH!!!! <i>*Bawls*.</i></font>\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Cam_Grave_702_11_23]</i>\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "We're here, her grave.\nAfter all that, I spent all my money just to meet with The Eye of Horus...\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "<i>*Sniffs*... *Sniffs*...</i>\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "... Kaori?\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "<i>*Sobs*</i>... I... I remember now. Why... Why did I forget... such an important person... Grandma Feng! WAAHHHHH!! <i>*Bawls*</i>.\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": ".....\nSo you remember? Thank goodness... You... you're indeed Kaori. Grandma always believed that you were still alive, even until the very end... Grandma, I wasn't lying. See, Kaori is here... I found her.\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<i>*Sniffs*</i>... NEKO will... leave you two alone for a while. Take your time.\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos5701"], "content": ""}, {"id": 56, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_???_697_12_25]</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "たった一人か？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "そうです！僕一人の仕業です！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "……なんだ？まだ子供じゃないか。\nこんなことのために私をわざわざ呼び出したのか？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "チーフ！\n確かに毎回盗られている品は大したことありませんが、このように毎月毎月少しずつ減っているなんて、虎盛堂の奴らの仕業に違いありません！\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "だからなんだ？\n奴らがコソコソしているのは知っている。\nだが、奴らが我々の部品を手にしたところで、それを使いこなす技術がなければ、こちらの脅威にはなり得ない。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "……では……こいつはどうしますか。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "どうするも何も……\n殺すも逃がすも勝手にすればいい。\nおい、名前は。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "は、隼人です。……楠隼人（クス ハヤト）。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "………\nどこかで聞いた事のある名だな。\n……付いてきなさい。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "やはりな。\nお前の保護者はコウ・ホウという名前だろう。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……！はい……どうして……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "これだ。\n我々の新医療プロジェクトの候補者リストの中に名前がある。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "医療プロジェクト……？\n僕、あなたたちは裏社会の組織なんだと思ってました。\n玖凰會と8羽のカラス……名前は聞いた事があります。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "我々は裏社会の組織で間違いない。\nだが、Node03の組織は全て裏社会の組織と言ってもいいだろう。\n君が普段使っている科学技術は誰が管理局に提供していると思っている？\nこの街を管理するのも、我々の仕事なのだ。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "君のおばあさんは、脳卒中だったな。\n未だに目を覚ましていない。\n彼女の容態は、ちょうど私たちの求めている被験者条件に当てはまる。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……本当ですか！？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "だが、これはまだ実験段階のプロジェクトだ。\n価格も危険性も高い。\n誰も被験者になりたがらないんだよ。\n被験者がいない限りこのプロジェクトは続けられない。\n……どうだ？君のおばあさんを被験者にすることに同意してくれるなら、今回の件は目を瞑ってやろう。\n\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_???_698_03_18]</i>\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["医療スタッフ"], "content": "申し訳ありません。\nおばあさまの脳神経は損傷が激しく、実験は失敗に終わりました。\nですが、完全に失敗したわけではありません。\n視覚以外の五感を取り戻させることはできました。\nこちらで、会話することができます。\nおばあさまの言葉は文字と合成音声で再生されます。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……！？すぐに起動してください！\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["医療スタッフ"], "content": "先ほども申し上げたとおり……実験は失敗しました。\n今起動すれば、2分ほどでその命は尽きてしまいます……\nですが、こうして放っておいても、安全とは言い切れません。\n決定権はあなたにあります。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……！\n……ううっ……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り 30 分»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……決めました……\n起動してください。\nでも、その前に看護師さんにお願いがあります……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Feng]"], "content": "ここは……？ここはどこだい？真っ暗じゃないか……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "おばあちゃん！\n僕だよ。隼人だよ。\n分かる？今、おばあちゃんの手を握ってるんだ。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Feng]"], "content": "<i>隼人……</i>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Bottle_Open", "瓶を開ける"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Feng]"], "content": "<i>この匂い……薫かい？\n……薫なのかい！？薫は……っ……どこに……！</i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Kaori]"], "content": "<i>おばあちゃん！</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["看護師"], "content": "……手を握る。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Feng]"], "content": "<i>薫！\nあぁ……隼人、薫が見つかったんだね。\n薫、よく帰ってきたね……\n……手のぬくもりを感じるよ……</i>\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["看護師"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "おばあちゃん、薫が帰ってきたよ。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Feng]"], "content": "<i>薫は強い子だ……だから絶対に生きてるって……分かっていたよ……隼人なら、薫を見つけてくれるってねぇ……\n……あぁ……あぁ……よかった……本当に……よかった……</i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "うん。\nだから、おばあちゃんは何も心配しなくていいんだ。\n毎日泣きながら寝る必要はもうないんだよ。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Feng]"], "content": "<i>よかっ……た…………よ……かっ……</i>\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["医療スタッフ"], "content": "時間です……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">これで笑顔で眠れるね……これでやっと……永遠に……っ……\nああ……</font><font size=\"3.6\">うわあああああ！！！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Cam_Grave_702_11_23]</i>\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "着いたよ。\nここがホウおばあちゃんのお墓だ。\nあれから、僕は全財産をはたいてホルスの目に会いに行ったんだ……\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "うっ……ぅぅ……\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……薫？\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "ぅぅ……私……私、思い出した……\n……なんで忘れてたの……こんな大事な人を……ホウおばあちゃん！\nうっ……うわあああああ！！\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "………\n思い出した？\nよかった……君は……やっぱり薫なんだね。\nおばあちゃんは亡くなる直前まで薫は生きてるって信じてた……\nおばあちゃん、僕、嘘はついてないよ。\nほら、見て。薫が帰ってきたんだ……僕、薫を見つけたんだよ……！\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "うう……NEKO……向こう行ってるね……ゆっくりしてきて……\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos5701"], "content": ""}, {"id": 56, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_???_697_12_25]</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "只有一個人？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "對，只有我一個！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "……什麼啊？不就是個小鬼嗎？別因為這種小事把我叫來倉庫。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "組長！雖然是叫小混混偷些無關緊要的貨，但每個月這樣一點一點地少，一定是虎盛堂的人幹的好事！\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "又怎樣？我一直知道他們在做這種偷雞摸狗的把戲。就算拿了我們的零件，他們也沒有技術對我們造成威脅。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "……那……這傢伙怎麼辦？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "什麼怎麼辦？看要處理掉還是放他走都隨便你們。喂，你叫什麼名字？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "隼、隼人……楠隼人。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "……。\n好像在哪看過這個名字……小鬼，跟我過來一下。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "果然，你的監護人，是黃芳對吧？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……！是的……請問你怎麼會……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "喏，她在我們最新的醫療計畫的候選名單裡。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "醫療計畫……？我還以為你們是黑社會，玖凰會跟八隻烏鴉……我多少聽過一點。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "我們是黑社會沒錯，但整個 Node 03 都是黑社會。你以為你平常在用的科技是誰提供給管理局的？管理城市也是我們工作的一環。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "你奶奶，是腦中風吧？現在昏迷不醒。她的情況，剛好符合我們最新科技實驗對象的條件，也許有辦法讓她醒過來。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……真的嗎！？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "但，這是一項還在實驗階段的不穩定項目，價格跟風險都太高了，沒有人願意嘗試，我們也就無法繼續。\n……怎麼樣？如果你願意簽署讓她擔任我們的實驗對象，我就當作沒看見你偷東西這回事。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_???_698_03_18]</i>\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["醫療人員"], "content": "抱歉，你奶奶的腦神經損毀得太嚴重，實驗失敗了。不過也不是完全失敗，我們成功還原了她視覺以外的感官。你可以透過這個介面跟她互動，她的想法會用文字和合成語音表示出來。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……！？請馬上啟動它！\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["醫療人員"], "content": "我剛剛說了吧……實驗失敗了。現在啟動，她將只有兩分鐘的壽命……不過就算這樣放著，也不知道她什麼時候會走，決定權在你。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……！\n……嗚……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉 30 分鐘»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "我……決定好了……\n請啟動吧，但是在那之前，我想請護士小姐幫我一個忙……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉 »»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Feng]"], "content": "<i>這裡是……？哪裡？好黑……</i>\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "奶奶！是我，隼人。感覺得到嗎？我的手。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Feng]"], "content": "<i>隼人……</i>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Bottle_Open", "打開瓶子"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Feng]"], "content": "<i>這個……味道……是薰？……是薰嗎！？妳在哪裡！？</i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Kaori]"], "content": "<i>奶奶！</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["護士"], "content": "……（握手）\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Feng]"], "content": "<i>薰！隼人找到妳了？妳回來了？我……感覺得到……妳的手……</i>\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["護士"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……奶奶，薰回來了喔。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Feng]"], "content": "<i>我就知道……妳是個勇敢的女孩，妳一定還活著……隼人一定會找到妳……啊……太好了……</i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "嗯，所以妳可以不用再擔心了。不用每晚都流著淚入睡了……\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Feng]"], "content": "<i>太……好了……太……好……</i>\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["醫療人員"], "content": "時間……到了。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">妳可以……帶著笑容入睡了，終於可以永遠……嗚嗚……</font><font size=\"3.6\">嗚嗚啊啊啊啊啊！！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Cam_Grave_702_11_23]</i>\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "我們到了，她的墳墓。\n那之後我用掉所有的錢去找了荷魯斯……\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗚……嗚嗚……\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……薰？\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗚嗚……我……我想起來了，為什麼……為什麼會忘記……這麼重要的人……芳奶奶！嗚嗚啊啊啊啊！！\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……。\n想起來了嗎？太好了……妳……果然是薰。奶奶一直到最後都認為妳活著……奶奶，我沒有說謊喔，妳看，薰來了……我找到她了。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "嗚嗚……NEKO 先……去旁邊一下好了，你們慢慢來。\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos5701"], "content": ""}, {"id": 56, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_???_697_12_25]</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "한 사람이라고?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "네! 저 혼자입니다!\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "...뭐야? 아직 어린 녀석이잖아? 고작 이런 일로 날 창고로 불러내지 마라.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 D"], "content": "주임님! 도둑맞은 수량이 많지 않은 건 사실이지만, 그래도 이렇게 매달 조금씩 줄어들고 있는 걸 보면, 분명 호성당놈들의 짓일 겁니다!\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "그게 무슨 문제가 된다는 거지? 그 녀석들이 줄곧 이런 좀도둑 짓 따위를 할 거라는 건 진작에 알고 있었다. 우리 부품을 빼돌렸다고 해도, 그쪽에는 우리에게 위협을 가할만한 기술력 따윈 가지고 있지도 않아.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 D"], "content": "...그렇다면... 이 녀석은 어떻게 처리할까요?\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "뭘 어떻게 처리해? \n죽이든 풀어주든 너희들이 알아서 해!\n거기 너, 이름이 뭐지?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "H... Ha... Hayato라고 합니다!\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "......\n어디선가 들어본 이름 같군...\n꼬맹이, 날 따라와라.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "역시... 네 보호자의 이름이 황팡, 맞나?\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": ".......! 네... 그걸 어떻게...\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "이걸 봐라.\n그 사람은 최근 우리 의료 프로젝트의 후원 명단에 올라갔지.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "의료 프로젝트...?\n전 당신들이 나쁜 조직인 줄로만 알고 있었는데...\n구황회와 8마리의 까마귀라고... 예전에 들어봤어요.\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "네 말대로 우린 지하 조직의 일부다. 하지만 Node 03 자체가 이미 커다란 암흑 조직인 셈이지. 네가 일상에서 아무렇지 않게 사용하는 기술들을 누가 관리국에게 제공했을 것 같으냐? 이 도시를 관리하고 있는 것도 바로 우리들이다.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "네 할머니는 뇌졸증이지, 아마?\n지금도 혼수상태로 깨어나지 못하고 있고. 지금 네 할머니의 상태는, 우리가 현재 찾고 있는 실험 대상자의 조건에 모두 부합하고 있다. 아마 네 할머니를 깨울 수 있을지도 모른다.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "...정말입니까!?\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "하지만 아직 실험 단계인 프로젝트일 뿐이다. 가격도, 위험성도 그만큼 높다고 할 수 있지. 그래서 아무도 실험 대상자가 되려 하질 않아.\n실험자가 없는 한, 이 프로젝트는 지속될 수 없어. \n...어때? 네 할머니를 실험 대상자로 선정하는 것에 동의만 해 준다면, 오늘 일은 못 본 셈 쳐주겠다.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": ".....!\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_???_698_03_18]</i>\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["의료원"], "content": "죄송합니다. 할머니의 뇌신경의 손상 상태가 너무 심각해서 실험은 실패로 끝났습니다. \n하지만 완전히 실패로 끝난 것만은 아닙니다. 시각 이외에 다른 감각들을 살려내는 데엔 성공했으니까요.\n이 인터페이스를 통해 할머니와 대화할 수 있습니다. 할머니의 생각이 문자와 합성 음성으로 표시될 겁니다.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "......!? 그럼 빨리 그것 좀 작동시켜 주세요!\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["의료원"], "content": "아까 말씀드린 대로... 실험은 실패로 끝났기 때문에... 지금 저것을 가동하면 할머니의 수명은 대략 2분 정도밖에 남지 않게 됩니다... 하지만 이대로 방치한다고 해도 언제 수명을 다하실지는 알 수 없습니다.\n결정권은 당신한테 있습니다.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": ".......!\n....흐...흐흑....\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»30분 앞으로 빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "저... 결정했어요...\n그것을 작동시켜 주세요. 하지만 그전에, 간호사분들께 부탁드리고 싶은 게 있습니다.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Feng]"], "content": "여기는...? 어디지? 어두워...\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "할머니! 저예요, Hayato. 느껴지세요? 제 손...\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Feng]"], "content": "<i>Hayato...</i>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Bottle_Open", "병뚜껑을 연다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Feng]"], "content": "<i>이건... 이 냄새는... Kaori?... Kaori니!? 지금 어딨니!?</i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Kaori]"], "content": "<i>할머니!</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["간호사"], "content": "......(손을 잡는다)\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Feng]"], "content": "<i>Kaori! Hayato가 찾아낸 거니? 드디어 돌아온 게야? 느껴지는구나... 네 손...</i>\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["간호사"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "....할머니, Kaoir가 돌아왔어요.\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Feng]"], "content": "<i>알고 있단다... 넌 아주 용감한 아이라서 분명 살아있을 거라고.... Hayato도 꼭 널 찾아낼 거라고 믿고 있었단다.... 하아... 정말 다행이야...</i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "네. \n그러니 이제 걱정 안 하셔도 돼요.\n이제 매일 밤 뒤척거리시면서 잠 못 드시는 일은 없을 거예요...\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Feng]"], "content": "<i>다행....이야... 정말... 다.... 행...이야...</i>\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["의료원"], "content": "시간 다 됐습니다...\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">이제... 편하게 잠드실 수 있어요... 드디어... 영원히...\n흐흑... 흐아아아아아앙!!!</font>\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Cam_Grave_702_11_23]</i>\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "도착했어. \n여기가 할머니의 무덤이야.\n그날 이후 난 전 재산을 털어서 호루스의 눈을 찾아갔었어...\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "흑... 흐흑...\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "......Kaori?\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "흐흑... 나... 기억났어... 왜... 왜 잊어버린 거야... 이런 소중한 사람을.... 팡 할머니!!!! 흐아아아아아앙!!\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "......\n기억났구나... 잘 됐다... 너는... 역시... Kaori가 맞았어.... 할머니는 마지막까지 네가 살아있다고 믿고 계셨어.... 할머니... 거짓말 아니라고 했죠? 보세요... 진짜... Kaori가 진짜로 돌아왔잖아요... 드디어... 찾아냈어요...\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "흑흑... NEKO는 우선... 다른 데에 가 있을 게... 함께 천천히 얘기 나누다가 와...\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos5701"], "content": ""}, {"id": 56, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_???_697_12_25]</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "只有一個人？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "對，只有我一個！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "……什麼啊？不就是個小鬼嗎？別因為這種小事把我叫來倉庫。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "組長！雖然是叫小混混偷些無關緊要的貨，但每個月這樣一點一點地少，一定是虎盛堂的人幹的好事！\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "又怎樣？我一直知道他們在做這種偷雞摸狗的把戲。就算拿了我們的零件，他們也沒有技術對我們造成威脅。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "……那……這傢伙怎麼辦？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "什麼怎麼辦？看要處理掉還是放他走都隨便你們。喂，你叫什麼名字？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "隼、隼人……楠隼人。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "……。\n好像在哪看過這個名字……小鬼，跟我過來一下。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "果然，你的監護人，是黃芳對吧？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……！是的……請問你怎麼會……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "喏，她在我們最新的醫療計畫的候選名單裡。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "醫療計畫……？我還以為你們是黑社會，玖凰會跟八隻烏鴉……我多少聽過一點。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "我們是黑社會沒錯，但整個 Node 03 都是黑社會。你以為你平常在用的科技是誰提供給管理局的？管理城市也是我們工作的一環。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "你奶奶，是腦中風吧？現在昏迷不醒。她的情況，剛好符合我們最新科技實驗對象的條件，也許有辦法讓她醒過來。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……真的嗎！？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "但，這是一項還在實驗階段的不穩定項目，價格跟風險都太高了，沒有人願意嘗試，我們也就無法繼續。\n……怎麼樣？如果你願意簽署讓她擔任我們的實驗對象，我就當作沒看見你偷東西這回事。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_???_698_03_18]</i>\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["醫療人員"], "content": "抱歉，你奶奶的腦神經損毀得太嚴重，實驗失敗了。不過也不是完全失敗，我們成功還原了她視覺以外的感官。你可以透過這個介面跟她互動，她的想法會用文字和合成語音表示出來。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……！？請馬上啟動它！\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["醫療人員"], "content": "我剛剛說了吧……實驗失敗了。現在啟動，她將只有兩分鐘的壽命……不過就算這樣放著，也不知道她什麼時候會走，決定權在你。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……！\n……嗚……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉 30 分鐘»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "我……決定好了……\n請啟動吧，但是在那之前，我想請護士小姐幫我一個忙……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉 »»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Feng]"], "content": "<i>這裡是……？哪裡？好黑……</i>\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "奶奶！是我，隼人。感覺得到嗎？我的手。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Feng]"], "content": "<i>隼人……</i>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Bottle_Open", "打開瓶子"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Feng]"], "content": "<i>這個……味道……是薰？……是薰嗎！？妳在哪裡！？</i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Kaori]"], "content": "<i>奶奶！</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["護士"], "content": "……（握手）\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Feng]"], "content": "<i>薰！隼人找到妳了？妳回來了？我……感覺得到……妳的手……</i>\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["護士"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……奶奶，薰回來了喔。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Feng]"], "content": "<i>我就知道……妳是個勇敢的女孩，妳一定還活著……隼人一定會找到妳……啊……太好了……</i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "嗯，所以妳可以不用再擔心了。不用每晚都流著淚入睡了……\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Feng]"], "content": "<i>太……好了……太……好……</i>\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["醫療人員"], "content": "時間……到了。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">妳可以……帶著笑容入睡了，終於可以永遠……嗚嗚……</font><font size=\"3.6\">嗚嗚啊啊啊啊啊！！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Cam_Grave_702_11_23]</i>\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "我們到了，她的墳墓。\n那之後我用掉所有的錢去找了荷魯斯……\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗚……嗚嗚……\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……薰？\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗚嗚……我……我想起來了，為什麼……為什麼會忘記……這麼重要的人……芳奶奶！嗚嗚啊啊啊啊！！\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……。\n想起來了嗎？太好了……妳……果然是薰。奶奶一直到最後都認為妳活著……奶奶，我沒有說謊喔，妳看，薰來了……我找到她了。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "嗚嗚……NEKO 先……去旁邊一下好了，你們慢慢來。\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos5701"], "content": ""}, {"id": 56, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_???_697_12_25]</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "只有一个人？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "对，只有我一个！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "……什么啊？不就是个小鬼吗？别因为这种小事把我叫来仓库。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["组员 D"], "content": "组长！虽然是叫小混混偷些无关紧要的货，但每个月这样一点一点地少，一定是虎盛堂的人干的好事！\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "又怎样？我一直知道他们在做这种偷鸡摸狗的把戏。就算拿了我们的零件，他们也没有技术对我们造成威胁。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["组员 D"], "content": "……那……这家伙怎么办？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "什么怎么办？看要处理掉还是放他走都随便你们。喂，你叫什么名字？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "隼、隼人……楠隼人。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "……。\n好像在哪看过这个名字……小鬼，跟我过来一下。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快转»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "果然，你的监护人，是黄芳对吧？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……！是的……请问你怎么会……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "喏，她在我们最新的医疗计画的候选名单里。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "医疗计画……？我还以为你们是黑社会，玖凰会跟八只乌鸦……我多少听过一点。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "我们是黑社会没错，但整个 Node 03 都是黑社会。你以为你平常在用的科技是谁提供给管理局的？管理城市也是我们工作的一环。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "你奶奶，是脑中风吧？现在昏迷不醒。她的情况，刚好符合我们最新科技实验对象的条件，也许有办法让她醒过来。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……真的吗！ ？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "但，这是一项还在实验阶段的不稳定项目，价格跟风险都太高了，没有人愿意尝试，我们也就无法继续。\n……怎么样？如果你愿意签署让她担任我们的实验对象，我就当作没看见你偷东西这回事。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_???_698_03_18]</i>\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["医疗人员"], "content": "抱歉，你奶奶的脑神经损毁得太严重，实验失败了。不过也不是完全失败，我们成功还原了她视觉以外的感官。你可以透过这个介面跟她互动，她的想法会用文字和合成语音表示出来。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……！ ？请马上启动它！\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["医疗人员"], "content": "我刚刚说了吧……实验失败了。现在启动，她将只有两分钟的寿命……不过就算这样放着，也不知道她什么时候会走，决定权在你。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……！\n……呜……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快转 30 分钟»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "我……决定好了……\n请启动吧，但是在那之前，我想请护士小姐帮我一个忙……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快转 »»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Feng]"], "content": "<i>这里是……？哪里？好黑……</i>\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "奶奶！是我，隼人。感觉得到吗？我的手。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Feng]"], "content": "<i>隼人……</i>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Bottle_Open", "打开瓶子"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Feng]"], "content": "<i>这个……味道……是薰？ ……是薰吗！ ？妳在哪里！ ？ </i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Kaori]"], "content": "<i>奶奶！ </i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["护士"], "content": "……（握手）\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Feng]"], "content": "<i>薰！隼人找到妳了？妳回来了？我……感觉得到……妳的手……</i>\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["护士"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……奶奶，薰回来了喔。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Feng]"], "content": "<i>我就知道……妳是个勇敢的女孩，妳一定还活着……隼人一定会找到妳……啊……太好了……</i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "嗯，所以妳可以不用再担心了。不用每晚都流着泪入睡了……\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Feng]"], "content": "<i>太……好了……太……好……</i>\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["医疗人员"], "content": "时间……到了。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">妳可以……带着笑容入睡了，终于可以永远……呜呜……</font><font size=\"3.6\">呜呜啊啊啊啊啊！ ！ ！ </font>\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Cam_Grave_702_11_23]</i>\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "我们到了，她的坟墓。\n那之后我用掉所有的钱去找了荷鲁斯……\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "呜……呜呜……\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……薰？\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "呜呜……我……我想起来了，为什么……为什么会忘记……这么重要的人……芳奶奶！呜呜啊啊啊啊！ ！\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……。\n想起来了吗？太好了……妳……果然是薰。奶奶一直到最后都认为妳活着……奶奶，我没有说谎喔，妳看，薰来了……我找到她了。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "呜呜……NEKO 先……去旁边一下好了，你们慢慢来。\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos5701"], "content": ""}, {"id": 56, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}